            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[伤心]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/l_shangxin-49b2fe44a6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>情绪激动可能导致心脏骤停】中国科学院院士王建安表示，人在过度悲伤、情绪激动的时候，神经会高度兴奋，儿茶酚胺等物质会释放，对心脏造成刺激可能导致心肌梗死，甚至心脏骤停<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻（CCTV生活圈）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4986880534446095" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">CCTV生活圈的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/713e54f1ly1hliwg9eiwpj20u01hcwhj.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/UssnuW54lx08bvqGZTle01041200d7Lw0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1704777351&amp;ssig=f6BVWIOuor&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/OiREA9Kklx08bvqGwyEE010412007UWK0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1704777351&amp;ssig=r2mTOo3p7Y&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/In4i8maKlx08bvqGn9Ta010412004kwq0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1704777351&amp;ssig=0ciqsOMnac&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4986880534446095" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
